title: Morton High School dedicates Joal Stanfield Tennis Complex
text:
Morton High School dedicates Joal Stanfield Tennis Complex 
By WEEK Reporter October 4, 2015 Updated Oct 4, 2015 at 8:55 PM CDT 
Morton High School has a brand new state of the art tennis complex. The complex was designed by Joal Stanfield, the Morton High tennis coach who died one year ago. Today, the complex was dedicated in the name of Joal.
